4Geeks Academy offers a course titled "Become an AI Machine Learning Engineer". This course is designed for individuals with no previous knowledge in the field and aims to help them start a career as a data scientist. The course duration is 16 weeks and includes three classes per week. The class size is limited to a maximum of 12 people. Upon completion, students receive a certificate recognized by multiple organizations. There are no prerequisites for taking this course, and it is available in both English and Spanish. The course covers topics such as Python, SQL, Looker, Streamlit, statistics, and various machine learning algorithms. Students will also have the opportunity to work on real-life case studies and develop their own AI projects. The instructors for this course include Sayyed Nezhadi, Francesco Pugliese, and Manuel Mena. More information about the course can be found on the 4Geeks Academy website: [https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/datascience-machine-learning](https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/datascience-machine-learning). stop